==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ladyship
<hw>La"dy*ship</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The rank or
position of a lady; -- given as a title (preceded by <xex>her</xex> or
<xex>your</xex>).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Your <qex>ladyship</qex> shall observe their gravity.</q>
<rj><qau>B. Jonson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lady's laces</ent>⟦br⟧
